com.mydogspies.xflymetar.data

Interface AirportCodeIO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Metar, Taf

    public interface AirportCodeIO
    A tiny utility interface so that we can extract ICAO code from any of data objects without having to know the object type. Used with fetchAPIData() method in the MainActivity together with the currentAPIData map.
